{"type":"message","id":"86cb32a6","parentId":"c262a1e1","timestamp":"2026-03-24T03:00:09.659Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，JSON 内容备份到文档也成功了。现在让我更新研究日志，并完成最终报告。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5ba85b31749a489dad1bbef1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\memory\\飞书备份研究日志.md","oldText":"### 方案 C：云盘 JSON 文件备份\n\n**思路：** 将备份数据序列化为 JSON，上传到云盘\n\n**API：** drive:file:upload（通过 feishu_drive）\n\n**待测试：** 实际调用","newText":"### 方案 C：云文档 JSON 内容备份\n\n**思路：** 将备份数据序列化为 JSON，写入云文档（代码块格式）\n\n**API：** feishu_doc action=create\n\n**结果：** ✅ **成功！**\n\n**创建的文档：**\n- document_id: `J0GUdQB9poumzjxrFMzcNB6snPe`\n- URL: https://feishu.cn/docx/J0GUdQB9poumzjxrFMzcNB6snPe\n- 内容格式：JSON 代码块\n\n**优势：**\n- 原始数据保真（JSON 格式）\n- 易于程序解析和恢复\n- 支持版本对比（diff）\n- 可压缩减少存储空间\n\n**劣势：**\n- 人工可读性较差\n- 需要解析才能查看内容\n\n**注：** feishu_drive 无直接 upload 动作，使用 feishu_doc 写入 JSON 内容是等效方案。"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774321179287}}
